00:51:58.310 --> 00:52:00.620
AUDIENCE: So you had
a slide up there about

00:52:00.620 --> 00:52:04.542
how different races
affect empathy.

00:52:04.542 --> 00:52:05.250
HOWARD ROSS: Yes.

00:52:05.250 --> 00:52:08.310
AUDIENCE: Have there
ever been studies done on

00:52:08.310 --> 00:52:11.410
does the type of like
the differences in races,

00:52:11.410 --> 00:52:12.980
like different
types of races, how

00:52:12.980 --> 00:52:15.320
that affects the
